955
00:56:19,107 --> 00:56:20,904
I saw Ho Chun lying on the ground,

956
00:56:21,109 --> 00:56:22,701
with blood all over his body.

957
00:56:22,944 --> 00:56:25,936
Foon pointed a gun at him and laughed.

958
00:56:26,047 --> 00:56:27,844
He said,
"Ho Chun, you are dead meat now."

959
00:56:28,049 --> 00:56:28,845
