01:01:25,546 --> 01:01:28,344
It's alright, count on me.

1063
01:01:32,486 --> 01:01:34,681
Don't worry, count on me.

1064
01:01:39,126 --> 01:01:41,321
Brother Lone doesn't seem to be alright

1065
