Your Honour,
I would like to summon a new witness.

1066
01:01:46,967 --> 01:01:48,559
What big deal?

1067
01:01:48,836 --> 01:01:50,030
Your old man!

1068
01:01:50,237 --> 01:01:51,636
Objection, how dare he scold my old man?

1069
01:01:51,872 --> 01:01:56,070
Come on, don't always object,
can you listen his words first?

1070
01:01:56,377 --> 01:01:58,971
Summon Sir Ho Sai.

1071
01:01:59,180 --> 01:02:00,579
I mean your dad!

1072
01:02:10,791 --> 01:02:12,190
This is my master.

1073
01:02:13,661 --> 01:02:15,060
Chan Mon-gut.

1074
01:02:15,229 --> 01:02:17,424
Sir, thank you for your help.

1075
01:02:35,816 --> 01:02:39,013
Please follow me.
I swear with my sincerity.

1076
01:02:42,089 --> 01:02:44,683
Sir, do you know the accused Ho Foon?

1077
01:02:44,892 --> 01:02:45,881
No.

1078
01:02:46,127 --> 01:02:50,723
But he is like my concubine Yu-fa.

1079
01:02:51,832 --> 01:02:52,821
What?

1080
01:02:53,067 --> 01:02:55,467
You have had a son
with your concubine?

1081
01:02:56,270 --> 01:02:59,467
Yes, we have a son named Nim-sai.

1082
01:03:00,274 --> 01:03:03,266
But he is dead.

1083
01:03:04,044 --> 01:03:05,636
Why?

1084
01:03:06,480 --> 01:03:07,674
I don't know.

1085
01:03:07,781 --> 01:03:09,180
Why don't you know that?

1086
01:03:09,383 --> 01:03:11,578
We've lost each other for over 20 years.

1087
01:03:11,719 --> 01:03:13,516
Why did you say he's dead?

1088
01:03:13,621 --> 01:03:15,418
I saw his dead body.

1089
01:03:15,623 --> 01:03:18,421
How could you confirm that was your son?

1090
01:03:18,692 --> 01:03:20,683
From his ass.

1091
01:03:20,895 --> 01:03:22,294
Ass?

1092
01:03:22,463 --> 01:03:23,259
Right,

1093
01:03:23,564 --> 01:03:27,557
I saw a triangular birthmark
on the body's ass.

1094
01:03:27,768 --> 01:03:29,963
That makes me believe that
was my son's dead body.

1095
01:03:30,704 --> 01:03:33,104
Sir, there are so many unexpected things
happened on earth.

1096
01:03:33,307 --> 01:03:34,706
For many things, you may not believe it.

1097
01:03:34,975 --> 01:03:37,170
Foon, do you want me to teach you?

1098
01:03:37,511 --> 01:03:38,705
Take off your pants! Now!

1099
01:03:38,879 --> 01:03:39,868
Yes!

1100
01:03:46,520 --> 01:03:47,714
How about the one I saw?

1101
01:03:47,988 --> 01:03:49,182
You just saw his ass, but not the face.

1102
01:03:49,456 --> 01:03:51,253
The birthmark may be drawn by someone.

1103
01:03:51,959 --> 01:03:53,551
It may be drawn by someone.

1104
01:03:53,827 --> 01:03:55,226
So you are my son?

1105
01:03:55,396 --> 01:03:57,796
I'm so glad to see you meeting your son!

1106
01:03:57,965 --> 01:03:58,954
Nim-sai!

1107
01:03:59,166 --> 01:04:03,967
Nim-sai...

1108
01:04:06,807 --> 01:04:09,401
Don't be too excited.

1109
01:04:09,543 --> 01:04:11,738
Men, come and take care of Sir Ho.

1110
01:04:14,949 --> 01:04:15,938
So, you've seen,

1111
01:04:16,183 --> 01:04:18,174
Sir Ho admitted the accused as his son.

1112
01:04:18,419 --> 01:04:24,016
This may be a deliberate conspiracy,

1113
01:04:24,325 --> 01:04:27,522
a trap for a nullius filius.

1114
01:04:27,761 --> 01:04:29,752
But the witness didn't swear

1115
01:04:29,964 --> 01:04:31,556
in front of the Bible.

1116
01:04:31,832 --> 01:04:34,426
So, his words won't be accepted
by the court.

1117
01:04:34,602 --> 01:04:35,591
He swore.

1118
01:04:35,803 --> 01:04:38,601
His hands touched the Bible,
but he said nothing.

1119
01:04:38,806 --> 01:04:40,205
Alright, again.

1120
01:04:54,822 --> 01:04:57,017
Your Honour,
although such a sad thing happened,

1121
01:04:57,191 --> 01:04:58,988
the words of the witness said
before his death...

1122
01:04:59,260 --> 01:05:00,249
should be forgotten.

1123
01:05:00,461 --> 01:05:01,655
Nuts!

1124
01:05:01,829 --> 01:05:03,228
He did say the truth,
how can you deny it?

1125
01:05:04,999 --> 01:05:07,593
Sorry, law is law.

1126
01:05:07,768 --> 01:05:09,360
Not any word should be amended.

1127
01:05:09,503 --> 01:05:10,902
Chan Mon-gut, I can't help you.

1128
01:05:11,071 --> 01:05:13,869
Your Honour, you can!

1129
01:05:14,108 --> 01:05:15,905
You'd better learn again.

1130
01:05:16,677 --> 01:05:18,269
Your dad died,
and you don't even shed a tear.

1131
01:05:18,445 --> 01:05:19,844
I think I'd better learn from you.

1132
01:05:20,247 --> 01:05:22,442
It's all because of you!

1133
01:05:22,616 --> 01:05:23,605
My dad had heart disease.

1134
01:05:23,784 --> 01:05:25,775
If you didn't ask him to be witness,
he wouldn't have died.

1135
01:05:26,020 --> 01:05:27,214
You, murderer!

1136
01:05:28,522 --> 01:05:30,114
Your Honour, I am sorry.

1137
01:05:30,324 --> 01:05:33,725
My father died,
I can't control my emotion.

1138
01:05:46,840 --> 01:05:47,636
What's up?

1139
01:05:47,941 --> 01:05:49,340
Damn it! You pretend crying!

1140
01:05:49,576 --> 01:05:50,565
You bastard!

1141
01:05:50,778 --> 01:05:52,769
You don't even have tears in your eyes,
can you see it?

1142
01:05:52,980 --> 01:05:54,379
It's dry!

1143
01:05:54,915 --> 01:05:56,906
You are caught red-handed!

1144
01:05:57,084 --> 01:05:58,176
Why do you pretend crying?

1145
01:05:58,385 --> 01:05:59,579
To hell with you!

1146
01:06:00,854 --> 01:06:04,051
Hey, you'd better behave!

1147
01:06:04,258 --> 01:06:06,453
Wait, let me tell you a story.

1148
01:06:06,593 --> 01:06:10,791
Once upon a time,
there was a noble named Ho.

1149
01:06:11,065 --> 01:06:13,056
He had a son named Ho Chung.

1150
01:06:13,300 --> 01:06:17,703
Sir Ho was old,
his son would be his heir of course.

1151
01:06:17,938 --> 01:06:22,341
But, suddenly,
his nullius filius Ho Foon appeared.

1152
01:06:25,012 --> 01:06:27,207
Someone worried his status
would be affected.

1153
01:06:27,448 --> 01:06:29,643
So he sent his fellow Chun...

1154
01:06:29,817 --> 01:06:31,614
to kill that nullius filius.

1155
01:06:31,785 --> 01:06:33,377
But, Chun failed.

1156
01:06:33,520 --> 01:06:36,512
Someone just took this opportunity
to kill Chun.

1157
01:06:36,657 --> 01:06:40,650
And made that poor kid be the scapegoat.

1158
01:06:40,894 --> 01:06:45,695
That guy is really hard-hearted
and cold-blooded!

1159
01:06:50,838 --> 01:06:53,636
What do you think about my assumption?

1160
01:07:01,682 --> 01:07:04,082
Prosecutor, why do you laugh?

1161
01:07:04,718 --> 01:07:07,516
Because this is such a nonsense
and stupid story.

1162
01:07:07,588 --> 01:07:08,782
Nonsense and stupid, huh?

1163
01:07:09,089 --> 01:07:10,488
But you are all sweat!

1164
01:07:10,824 --> 01:07:12,416
It's really weird.

1165
01:07:14,628 --> 01:07:17,222
Prosecutor, where were you when
the homicide happened?

1166
01:07:17,431 --> 01:07:18,227
At home.

1167
01:07:18,499 --> 01:07:19,295
What were you doing?

1168
01:07:19,633 --> 01:07:20,224
Reading.

1169
01:07:20,367 --> 01:07:21,163
What book did you read?

1170
01:07:21,301 --> 01:07:21,892
A tale of two cities.

1171
01:07:22,102 --> 01:07:22,898
Where did you stop?

1172
01:07:23,003 --> 01:07:25,403
Well... the soldiers...

1173
01:07:25,706 --> 01:07:26,695
The soldiers met Snow White,
is that right?

1174
01:07:26,940 --> 01:07:27,929
Yes, they met Snow White...

1175
01:07:28,275 --> 01:07:30,675
No, you are fooling me!

1176
01:07:30,811 --> 01:07:34,008
Smart you! So, where did you stop?

1177
01:07:34,748 --> 01:07:35,737
Why should I answer your question?

1178
01:07:35,983 --> 01:07:37,382
Right, I don't know
why you want to answer me!

1179
01:07:37,684 --> 01:07:38,878
What a shame!

1180
01:07:39,119 --> 01:07:40,108
Chan Mon-gut, you've gone too far!

1181
01:07:40,254 --> 01:07:41,653
Wipe your sweat first!

1182
01:07:43,524 --> 01:07:46,322
I think you haven't had
good sleep lately.

1183
01:07:46,560 --> 01:07:48,960
Does Ho Chun visit you every night?

1184
01:07:49,163 --> 01:07:49,959
Your Honour!

1185
01:07:50,197 --> 01:07:50,788
Let's go back to our topic,

1186
01:07:51,064 --> 01:07:52,656
what did you do that night?

1187
01:07:52,833 --> 01:07:56,030
I told you, I read at home.

1188
01:07:56,203 --> 01:07:57,602
No, I don't mean
the night Chun was killed.

1189
01:07:57,871 --> 01:07:59,862
I mean the night
before he was killed.

1190
01:08:00,107 --> 01:08:01,904
Before killing him,
I went...

1191
01:08:06,547 --> 01:08:07,741
Yes!

1192
01:08:10,083 --> 01:08:11,482
You're finished!

1193
01:08:16,557 --> 01:08:18,548
Your Honour,
I request to reach the final address.

1194
01:08:18,826 --> 01:08:22,227
Damn you! Tell us what you did
on the night before Chun's death.

1195
01:08:23,797 --> 01:08:25,196
Police.

1196
01:08:29,636 --> 01:08:31,627
No! I mean Chan Mon-gut.

1197
01:08:32,339 --> 01:08:33,135
What's the matter?

1198
01:08:33,373 --> 01:08:37,571
The defence counsel's personal point
of view is really amazing!

1199
01:08:37,778 --> 01:08:39,973
But according to the legal procedure...

1200
01:08:40,147 --> 01:08:42,547
Come on! Why are you so stubborn?

1201
01:08:43,016 --> 01:08:45,211
You're charged with contempt of court.

1202
01:08:45,352 --> 01:08:49,948
I have to sent you to jail for one day.

1203
01:08:50,257 --> 01:08:51,656
Immediate execution.

1204
01:08:52,159 --> 01:08:53,558
Your Honour, are you kidding me?

1205
01:08:53,727 --> 01:08:55,524
Your Honour, can you give me face?

1206
01:08:55,696 --> 01:08:57,493
- Hubby.
- Are you kidding me?

1207
01:09:00,534 --> 01:09:02,331
Your Honour, for what we've just heard,

1208
01:09:02,603 --> 01:09:04,195
should we forget them too?

1209
01:09:04,505 --> 01:09:07,497
Since the statement
is against legal procedure,

1210
01:09:07,708 --> 01:09:12,304
Jury, you should forget
everything you've just heard.

1211
01:09:12,846 --> 01:09:15,644
Chan Mon-gut will be represented
by Wu Man.

1212
01:09:15,883 --> 01:09:18,078
Tomorrow, the final address
should be presented.

1213
01:09:18,385 --> 01:09:19,784
Court.

1214
01:09:57,558 --> 01:09:58,752
Brother Foon.

1215
01:09:59,192 --> 01:10:00,181
Miss Shui.

1216
01:10:00,594 --> 01:10:01,788
Why are you here?

1217
01:10:01,962 --> 01:10:03,361
I come to save you.

1218
01:10:03,497 --> 01:10:04,896
Alright, I'll pack up first.

1219
01:10:07,834 --> 01:10:09,631
I just want to prove your personality.

1220
01:10:10,437 --> 01:10:11,836
I am right.

1221
01:10:12,105 --> 01:10:15,302
You are a gutless coward.

1222
01:10:15,442 --> 01:10:16,431
What?

1223
01:10:16,977 --> 01:10:18,171
If you leave like this,

1224
01:10:18,478 --> 01:10:20,070
you will be sinful forever.

1225
01:10:20,280 --> 01:10:22,475
You can't live peacefully and you'd hide
up for the rest of your life.

1226
01:10:22,649 --> 01:10:24,844
You would be a criminal forever.

1227
01:10:27,287 --> 01:10:29,084
I have decided to stay.

1228
01:10:29,323 --> 01:10:30,722
That's why I love you.

1229
01:10:36,797 --> 01:10:38,196
Creep!

1230
01:10:39,266 --> 01:10:40,460
Ho Foon, someone comes to visit you.

1231
01:10:43,270 --> 01:10:44,669
Miss Shui.

1232
01:10:46,473 --> 01:10:47,667
Where did you cut your hair?

1233
01:10:47,908 --> 01:10:49,102
Number 9, Nathan Road.

1234
01:10:49,276 --> 01:10:51,073
Cut the crap, I won't go.

1235
01:10:51,278 --> 01:10:53,075
I am not a gutless coward.

1236
01:10:53,347 --> 01:10:54,746
If I leave like this, I will be sinful
for the rest of my life.

1237
01:10:54,848 --> 01:10:56,247
I won't live peacefully.

1238
01:10:56,383 --> 01:10:57,975
And I will be a criminal forever.

1239
01:10:58,218 --> 01:10:59,617
I won't leave.

1240
01:10:59,786 --> 01:11:01,981
I come to express my support.

1241
01:11:02,189 --> 01:11:03,588
You can't lose in this case.

1242
01:11:03,857 --> 01:11:06,052
Because your master's name
is so important.

1243
01:11:07,427 --> 01:11:08,826
But now, I know that,

1244
01:11:09,129 --> 01:11:11,927
you are a real brave and quixotic hero.

1245
01:11:13,467 --> 01:11:15,264
I believe that you are innocent.

1246
01:11:17,104 --> 01:11:18,298
I'll wait for you.

1247
01:11:18,438 --> 01:11:20,235
Good speech!

1248
01:11:22,509 --> 01:11:24,909
Will you wait for me?

1249
01:11:35,288 --> 01:11:36,482
You'll be released at 5 p.m. tomorrow.

1250
01:11:36,690 --> 01:11:38,487
How about the final address?

1251
01:11:38,825 --> 01:11:40,417
They can do nothing to me.

1252
01:11:40,594 --> 01:11:41,993
They can't imagine that,
you studied law in UK too.

1253
01:11:42,262 --> 01:11:43,854
Tomorrow, you'll take my place.

1254
01:11:44,197 --> 01:11:45,391
Hubby...

1255
01:11:45,666 --> 01:11:47,258
You'll handle Foon's life.

1256
01:11:47,467 --> 01:11:49,059
You sent me to study law in UK...

1257
01:11:49,336 --> 01:11:51,133
isn't it because you felt boring?

1258
01:11:51,405 --> 01:11:53,805
Of course not! The world is so big!

1259
01:11:54,041 --> 01:11:56,032
I think, it's a good deed...

1260
01:11:56,309 --> 01:11:58,903
to let you see the world, is that right?

1261
01:11:59,546 --> 01:12:02,140
Hubby, I didn't study law in UK.

1262
01:12:03,016 --> 01:12:04,608
They rejected me.

1263
01:12:05,452 --> 01:12:07,647
So, what did you study in UK?

1264
01:12:08,689 --> 01:12:10,281
Fashion design.

1265
01:12:10,524 --> 01:12:11,718
What did you say?

1266
01:12:11,858 --> 01:12:14,850
- Time's up.
- I studied fashion design.

1267
01:12:14,961 --> 01:12:16,553
Fashion design.

1268
01:12:16,797 --> 01:12:17,991
Hubby, what shall we do?

1269
01:12:18,198 --> 01:12:20,189
Fashion design?!

1270
01:12:24,337 --> 01:12:25,736
Court.

1271
01:12:32,813 --> 01:12:36,010
Prosecutor,
you can start your final address now.

1272
01:12:39,152 --> 01:12:41,143
Although sentiment counts beyond law.

1273
01:12:41,388 --> 01:12:43,982
One should be punished if he killed.

1274
01:12:44,357 --> 01:12:45,551
You'd better think.

1275
01:12:45,826 --> 01:12:47,225
If your family was killed,

1276
01:12:47,427 --> 01:12:48,826
what'll you do?

1277
01:12:48,929 --> 01:12:50,726
Now, all the evidences
which the court admitted,

1278
01:12:50,931 --> 01:12:54,332
prove Ho Foon is the murderer.

1279
01:12:54,568 --> 01:12:58,971
I request the jury would plead
Ho Foon guilty.

1280
01:13:00,340 --> 01:13:01,329
Defence counsel.

1281
01:13:05,345 --> 01:13:07,745
My husband paid me to study law in UK.

1282
01:13:08,014 --> 01:13:10,209
But I am so sorry to him,
I didn't study law.

1283
01:13:10,550 --> 01:13:12,347
I studied fashion design.

1284
01:13:15,589 --> 01:13:17,181
I am not well educated,

1285
01:13:17,424 --> 01:13:18,823
but I don't understand one thing.

1286
01:13:19,092 --> 01:13:22,084
What's more important?

1287
01:13:22,529 --> 01:13:24,520
Legal procedure or life?

1288
01:13:25,599 --> 01:13:28,193
Your Honour, if you don't mind me
telling my point of view.

1289
01:13:28,401 --> 01:13:31,393
I think that,
you've studied so many years of law,

1290
01:13:31,538 --> 01:13:33,529
you have got nothing at all.

1291
01:13:36,109 --> 01:13:38,907
Like my husband, I haven't studied law.

1292
01:13:39,679 --> 01:13:42,477
But I dare to open my eyes
to see what's right and wrong.

1293
01:13:43,216 --> 01:13:45,411
I am proud of my hubby.

1294
01:13:45,685 --> 01:13:47,084
I love him.

1295
01:13:47,921 --> 01:13:51,118
Jury, I believe that you are not nuts.

1296
01:13:51,224 --> 01:13:52,816
You should know how to judge.

1297
01:13:53,093 --> 01:13:55,084
If all of you are nuts,

1298
01:13:55,262 --> 01:13:56,854
it'll be useless to say anything.

1299
01:13:58,198 --> 01:13:59,597
Thank you very much.

1300
01:14:09,810 --> 01:14:11,004
You've been released!

1301
01:14:11,211 --> 01:14:12,007
Yes.

1302
01:14:12,145 --> 01:14:13,134
You heard everything?

1303
01:14:13,313 --> 01:14:14,109
Yes.

1304
01:14:14,247 --> 01:14:14,838
What do you think?

1305
01:14:15,115 --> 01:14:17,310
Excellent!

1306
01:14:20,554 --> 01:14:22,749
You're very much appreciated.

1307
01:14:23,256 --> 01:14:24,655
You are flattering me.

1308
01:14:24,925 --> 01:14:26,722
Of course not! Look.

1309
01:14:31,498 --> 01:14:34,296
The blind is being touched by you,
he is crying.

1310
01:14:34,601 --> 01:14:36,592
Your Honour, if there isn't anything
special, I request a rest.

1311
01:14:36,736 --> 01:14:39,933
For I have an eye problem.
You see pus from my eyes?

1312
01:14:48,882 --> 01:14:50,679
Jury, have you reached any verdict?

1313
01:14:50,917 --> 01:14:51,906
Yes.

1314
01:14:54,221 --> 01:14:55,415
Unanimous?

1315
01:14:55,522 --> 01:14:56,716
Yes.

1316
01:15:04,531 --> 01:15:06,931
The jury has pleaded the accused guilty.

1317
01:15:07,167 --> 01:15:11,160
As stipulated,

1318
01:15:15,275 --> 01:15:18,472
the accused should be hanged.

1319
01:15:34,194 --> 01:15:36,594
Court.

1320
01:15:49,709 --> 01:15:50,903
Wait.

1321
01:15:58,952 --> 01:16:01,352
