01:16:18,171 --> 01:16:19,160
Sir.

1324
01:17:05,785 --> 01:17:08,982
You kill me,
but many many Ho Foons will appear.

1325
01:17:11,992 --> 01:17:13,584
Sir.

1326
01:17:18,665 --> 01:17:19,859
Wait.

1327
01:17:20,133 --> 01:17:22,328
