1336
01:17:36,750 --> 01:17:37,944
Your Honour, law is law.

1337
01:17:38,184 --> 01:17:40,175
Not even one letter should be amended.

1338
01:17:40,387 --> 01:17:41,581
Now, I can't help you.

1339
01:17:42,422 --> 01:17:43,218
Your Honour!

1340
01:17:44,224 --> 01:17:45,623
Think before you speak.

1341
01:17:45,892 --> 01:17:47,484
Otherwise, you will lose the face
of British government.

1342
01:17:47,694 --> 01:17:49,685
And you may be charged with murdering.

1343
01:17:54,467 --> 01:17:56,264
I want an urgent meeting first.

1344
01:17:56,436 --> 01:17:57,630
Alright, back to your work.

1345
01:17:57,804 --> 01:17:58,793
You are all nuts!

1346
01:17:59,039 --> 01:18:00,028
Get lost.

1347
01:18:13,953 --> 01:18:15,147
It's my time!

1348
01:18:40,547 --> 01:18:41,946
The final decision
of the court has been reached.

1349
01:18:42,148 --> 01:18:43,547
