1354
01:19:07,574 --> 01:19:08,768
Brother Foon.

1355
01:19:08,908 --> 01:19:09,897
Lotus.

1356
01:19:10,243 --> 01:19:14,441
My dear baby, your sudden appearance...

1357
01:19:14,714 --> 01:19:18,309
makes me feel excited...

1358
01:19:20,820 --> 01:19:22,811
Closer...

1359
01:19:23,123 --> 01:19:26,320
I am ready. Alright?

1360
01:19:33,900 --> 01:19:35,492
