1366
01:19:45,011 --> 01:19:48,208
Master, Madam.

1367
01:19:48,448 --> 01:19:49,244
Foon.

1368
01:19:49,415 --> 01:19:50,006
Brother Foon.

1369
01:19:50,150 --> 01:19:50,946
Brother Gut.

1370
01:19:51,317 --> 01:19:52,306
