1375
01:19:57,724 --> 01:20:00,318
You are cultured!
You know Shakespeare too?

1376
01:20:00,593 --> 01:20:01,992
She's suitable to study
English literature.

1377
01:20:02,462 --> 01:20:04,259
That's good for her.

1378
01:20:04,764 --> 01:20:05,355
Foon.

1379
01:20:05,598 --> 01:20:06,587
Master.

1380
01:20:06,733 --> 01:20:08,530
