1390
01:20:29,289 --> 01:20:30,483
It's alright!

1391
01:20:30,790 --> 01:20:31,984
Number nine, Nathan Road?

1392
01:20:32,225 --> 01:20:34,022
Bastard, you look great.

1393
01:20:34,861 --> 01:20:36,453
Damn it, no big deal?

1394
